INSERT INTO `ba_chat` VALUES ('3062', '0', 'AI机器人', '以下是一个示例VBA代码，用于识别名为“考勤原始数据 - 副本”的Excel工作簿并将其内部的四个工作表中的透视表合并到名为“Sheet6”的工作表中：\n\n```\nSub MergePivotTables()\n    Dim origData As Worksheet, pivotTables() As Worksheet\n    Dim mergeTable As PivotTable\n    Dim i As Long, j As Long, count As Long\n    \n    Set origData = ThisWorkbook.Sheets(\"考勤原始数据 - 副本\")\n    pivotCount = 4\n    ReDim pivotTables(pivotCount)\n    \n    &#039;检查工作表是否存在\n    For i = 1 To pivotCount\n        name = Array(\"工时透视\", \"休假透视\", \"培训透视\", \"政府透视\")(i - 1)\n        Set pivotTables(i) = Nothing\n        For Each sheet In ThisWorkbook.Worksheets\n            If sheet.Name Like \"*\" &amp; name &amp; \"*\" Then\n                Set pivotTables(i) = sheet\n                Exit For\n            End If\n        Next\n        If pivotTables(i) Is Nothing Then\n            MsgBox \"工作表[\" &amp; name &amp; \"]不存在\"\n            Exit Sub\n        End If\n    Next\n\n    &#039;设置新的合并透视表位置\n    Set mergeTable = origData.PivotTableWizard(TableDestination:=origData.Range(\"A1\"))\n    mergeTable.PivotFields(\"部门\").Orientation = xlRowField\n    mergeTable.PivotFields(\"姓名\").Orientation = xlRowField\n    \n    &#039;将透视表添加到合并透视表中\n    For i = 1 To pivotCount\n        dataRange = pivotTables(i).ListObjects(1).Range\n        dataRange.Copy Destination:=mergeTable.TableRange1.Offset(mergeTable.TableRange1.Rows.Count, )\n        mergeTable.SourceData = mergeTable.TableRange1.Resize(mergeTable.TableRange1.Rows.Count + dataRange.Rows.Count - 1)\n        mergeTable.RefreshTable\n    Next\n\n    MsgBox \"合并完成\"\nEnd Sub\n```\n\n此代码将逐个扫描名为“考勤原始数据 - 副本”的Excel工作簿中的所有工作表，检查是否存在四个工作表中的任何一个。如果不存在任何一个，则会显示一条错误消息并退出程序。\n\n存在这四个工作表之一时，程序会在原始数据工作表的A1单元格创建新的透视表。然后，程序将逐个添加四个工作表中的透视表。每个透视表的数据源都将复制到新的合并透视表中，并在复制之后刷新新的合并透视表。当所有透视表都添加到新的合并透视表中后，程序最后会显示一条消息。请注意，您可能需要根据实际情况对代码进行修改。', '0', '0', 'gpt-3.5-turbo-0301', null, null, '1683017015');
